data.description: Relax and enjoy the vibes of Intracoastal living at 1024 Kokomo Key Lane, a bright and airy townhome in Delray Beach. With 2 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and 1,184 sq. ft. of remodeled space, you'll feel right at home in the sought after neighborhood of Kokomo Key. Enjoy exclusive access to a community dock/boardwalk, pool, boat storage, BBQ grills, and playground. The open kitchen and living area floor plan is designed for seamless entertaining--perfect for friends and family. Take a quick golf cart ride to the beach or explore the exciting nightlife of Atlantic Ave, just 2 minutes away. This isn't just a home; it's a lifestyle. Don't miss the chance to own a slice of coastal paradise!
